# Accuracy

![image-20190205092602492](/Users/denniszelada/Library/Application Support/typora-user-images/image-20190205092602492.png)

To calculate the accuracy on Sklearn we can use the command

```from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score accuracy_score(y_true, y_pred)```

